  "description": "The removal of 2 x antenna and supporting steelwork at 17m plus the removal of 2 x ancillary RRU Units from the rooftop of the exchange. These will be replaced by the installation of 4 x new antenna 1 x at 17m, 1 x at 17.8m, 1 x at 19m and 1 x at 19.8m utilising new support poles off existing supporting steelwork on the exchange building. There will also be the relocationof 1 x H3G and EE antenna at 17m and 1 x EE antenna at 18.86m and relocation of 4 x RRU Units utilising the new supporting steelwork. The 19m and 19.8m antenna will now sit proud of the current exchange roofline.  The removal of 1 x antenna at 17m and 1 x RRU plus supporting steelwork to be replaced with a 1 x new antenna at 17m and 1 x new antenna at 19m (Above the 17m antenna), utilising a new support pole. 2 x existing RRU's will be relocated to the rear of the new antenna on the new support pole. The 19m antenna will also sit proud of the exchange roofline. Ancillary works: - Feeder cable works, and refreshment works within the existing rooftop equipment cabinets.",
